      <title>Pick a Card</title>
      <link>/post/2020-10-29-cardtrick/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Oct 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/post/2020-10-29-cardtrick/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Everyone loves magic tricks - in some countries it&amp;rsquo;s a &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;legal&lt;/a&gt; requirement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Card tricks can be performed on stage..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./magacian.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Magician&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;..or explained in a &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BbnbfKbgf5Q&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;math video&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BbnbfKbgf5Q&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;MattParker.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;..but card tricks and in fact all magic tricks are at their &lt;em&gt;very&lt;/em&gt; best in blog form.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&#34;ordinary-deck&#34;&gt;Ordinary Deck&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an ordinary deck of cards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./ordinarydeck.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Ordinary&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I can make the deck change color before your eyes but oddly that is not the trick.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./fan.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;CardFan&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;time-to-choose&#34;&gt;Time to Choose&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pick a card, any card from this perfectly ordinary deck&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./featured.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Pick&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Look at your card
&lt;img src=&#34;./7hearts.png&#34; alt=&#34;Card&#34;&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Don&amp;rsquo;t show it to &lt;em&gt;anyone&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Place it back in the deck&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-art-of-deception&#34;&gt;The Art of Deception&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My assistant will now distract the audience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./Taylor-Swift-Magician-s-Assistant-taylor-swift-38438035-683-1024.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Reaction&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s not clear which is more surprising&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;that I need an assistant to do a card trick&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;that my assistant is somehow Taylor Swift&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-big-reveal&#34;&gt;The Big Reveal&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now for the big moment &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.freesoundslibrary.com/drum-roll-sound-effect/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;(drum roll)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is &lt;strong&gt;this&lt;/strong&gt; your card!?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;./7hearts.png&#34; alt=&#34;Reaction&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;..and that&amp;rsquo;s how it&amp;rsquo;s done ladies and gentlemen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank You&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
